Current State: The app is running on 127.0.0.1:5000 (Localhost).

Task:

Create a requirements.txt for Python.

Create a Procfile (if using Render/Heroku) using Gunicorn instead of the dev server.

Update React API calls to point to the production URL instead of localhost.

